      <h2>How to make an Egg Omelet </h2>
        <p>First you will crack your eggs into a bowl and whisk them. Take a pinch of salt and pepper for taste. Place a bot over a medium level fire. After few minutes, spray the cooking oil and place the eggs into pan. After 3 minutes of cooking eggs,place vegetables and cheese on a half side of eggs. Wait 2 more minutes and flip eggs. You are almost done! Let the egg simmer on to the vegetables and after a minute has gone you made your omelet!</p>
        <p>Ingredients — 1 cup of oats, 1/2 cup of milk or water, 1 serving of chocolate chips, a dash of cinnamon. Time elapsed - 3 minutes // Time prep - 1 minute</p>
